Air conditioning is an electronic device that consider highly significant to people specifically during summer. However, people may overuse it which might affect their performance while working or their health.
Overuse air conditioning in offices, classrooms and homes might have a detrimental impact on people. According to Hedge and Gaygen, if the room temperature is below average people will be less productive and less alarm which might impact their attention and increase the amount of mistakes they might do.
During summer people seek and are more attract by places that provide cold temperatures. Moreover "being able to make people feel cold in the summer is the sign of power and prestige. Therefore luxury stores have colder temperatures than mass-market stores" Murphy, 2015).
Therefore, the aim of using it is not sufficient.
To sum up, people should wisdomly use air conditioning and by attention to the detrimental impact that it might cause.